These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, eggplant, asparagus
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, filmmaking, baking
The people have 3 different jobs:  police-officer, analyst, scientist
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, ambient, soul
There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, malaysian, thai
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, climbing, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is the malaysian##1
 2. the person who's sport is skiing is the scientist##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is between the thai and the person drinking lemonade##2
 4. the fan of ambient is on the left of the japanese##1
 5. the analyst is the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is the japanese##1
 7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
 9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the analyst##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | lemonade    | almond-milk   | sprite           |
| Food          | eggplant       | asparagus    | lettuce         |
| Hobby         | filmmaking    | baking  | drawing        |
| Job           | police-officer | analyst   | scientist      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient        | soul    | reggae       |
| Nationality   | malaysian     | japanese  | thai       |
| Sport         | sailing     | climbing | skiing |

