.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, water
There 3 different types of food: kale, avocado, banana
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, family, thriller
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, soul, gospel
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, egyptian
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, hamster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, biathlon, basketball
 1. the owner of the hamster is the italian##1
 2. the owner of the hamster is the person watching thriller movies##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking tea##2
 5. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of salsa##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person eating kale is the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
10. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person eating banana##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | tea   | water    | mirinda         |
| Food          | kale    | avocado | banana          |
| Movie-Genre   | crime  | thriller  | family     |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | soul      | salsa         |
| Nationality   | egyptian      | italian   | french    |
| Pet           | chinchilla        | hamster      | hedgehog         |
| Sport         | biathlon | golf  | basketball |

