The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, skiing, rowing
 1. the person eating radish is the owner of the lizard##1
 2. the spanish is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 3. the person watching western movies is the person eating asparagus##1
 4. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the lizard##1
 5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the american and the fan of disco##2
 8. the american is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 9. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person eating radish##1
11. the american is the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
