 4. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
 5. the fan of d&b is between the person watching action movies and the person drinking water##2
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 7. the fan of d&b is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the chef is the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the person drinking iced-tea is between the chef and the fisherman##2
10. the german is on the left of the japanese##1

