 4. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is rugby and the fan of house##2
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the bird##2
 7. the person driving the subway is between the person eating pepper and the person drinking sprite##2
 8. the fan of gospel is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 9. the pilot is on the right of the fan of metal##1
10. the police-officer is the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
