 3. the mexican is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person watching mystery movies##1
 5. the person driving the roller is on the right of the mexican##1
 6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
