.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, pineapple, lime
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, chess, skydiving
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, freelancer, project-manager
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, 7upsy, time-travel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, cricket, vaning
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, bus, van
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the project-manager##1
2. the person driving the van is on the right of the person eating lime##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the doctor##1
4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is between the person watching martial-arts movies and the freelancer##2
5. the person eating lime is between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person eating lime##1
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
9. the person watching 7upsy movies is on the left of the doctor##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | 7up      | soy-milk      | almond-milk       |
| Food          | pineapple      | lime    | cucumber   |
| Hobby         | skydiving    | board-games     | chess     |
| Job           | freelancer    | doctor | project-manager   |
| Movie-Genre   | 7upsy    | time-travel    | martial-arts       |
| Sport         | vaning | lacrosse      | cricket    |
| Transport     | bus       | tram | van |

