.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: plum, lime, cabbage
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, card-games, video-games
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, romance, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: salsa, funk, gospel
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: soccer, lacrosse, weightlifting
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, train, bike
1. the person driving the train is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person eating lime is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's hobby is baking##2
6. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
7. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of funk##1
8. the person driving the airplane is the person watching adventure movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk       | water     | almond-milk         |
| Food          | plum     | lime      | cabbage     |
| Hobby         | card-games | video-games    | baking      |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts   | romance | adventure    |
| Music-Genre   | funk        | gospel     | salsa   |
| Sport         | soccer     | lacrosse | weightlifting |
| Transport     | train     | bike       | airplane    |

