.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: corn, mango, pomegranate
The people have 3 different jobs:  project-manager, photographer, chef
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, indonesian, chinese
3 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, bird
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, parkour, volleyball
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, ship
1. the person drinking sprite is the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person driving the ship is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the project-manager is between the person drinking iced-tea and the owner of the bird##2
4. the australian is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
5. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
7. the photographer is the person eating corn##1
8. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
9. the indonesian is between the person eating corn and the person driving the skateboard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta    | sprite       | iced-tea      |
| Food          | corn   | pomegranate   | mango  |
| Job           | photographer  | project-manager | chef    |
| Nationality   | australian   | indonesian     | chinese  |
| Pet           | bird     | hamster        | cat |
| Sport         | parkour | rugby   | volleyball  |
| Transport     | snowmobile    | ship     | skateboard      |

 